accessibility.text: The hospital room is so cold. May felt so lonely.

The Chinese New Year's festival is coming, and she missed her family more and more. She missed the food, missed her hometown friends, and everything else outside this room. Right now, she's so far away from all of them, which made her want to cry. She cried a little bit, until she decided that she has to talk to someone.
Call her parents at the other side of the earth
Call her friends in the United States, who are able to come to see her
